name: Artificer
description: Artificer is a DAO of developers, designers, creators, inventors. At Artificer DAO, makers gather in one online community to build crypto projects and help each other to achieve their goals through hackathons, grants and rewards. Artificer aims to incentivize makers in the crypto space, and bring web2 developers to web3 ecosystem. Artificer DAO has governance and treasury to support early stage projects.
